title: No Garen/Ashe Chest
body: Hey y'all, just started a new account and i didn't get an ashe and garen chest like i normally do. Whats up with that?

replies.body: You should be getting that premium chest once the account hits level 5. Hit me back up if you're level 5 and still don't have the premium chest!
Thanks, I did hit level 5 already but  i just got it, ty for helping though.
